---
// src/pages/index.astro
// No frontmatter needed for now — Astro will handle the layout
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Solvus | Built for US Real Estate Agents</title>
<meta name="description" content="Solvus builds custom websites for US real estate agents. Fast, owned, SEO-ready. Book a 20-minute call.">
<meta property="og:title" content="Solvus | Built for US Real Estate Agents">
<meta property="og:description" content="Custom-built. Fast. Yours to keep. Built specifically for US real estate agents who are done renting templates.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#03060C">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@100;200;300;400&family=Space+Mono:wght@400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
/* ============================================================
   TOKENS
   ============================================================ */
:root {
    --nav-h: 72px;
    --c-bg:        #03060C;
    --c-bg-light:  #0A111E;
    --c-white:     #F8FAFC;
    --c-cyan:      #00E5FF;
    --c-muted:     #4A5D7E;
    --c-light-bg:  #F8FAFC;
    --c-light-text:#03060C;
    --font-sans:  'Outfit', sans-serif;
    --font-mono:  'Space Mono', monospace;
    --ease-out:   cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    /* spacing scale */
    --s1: 0.5rem; --s2: 1rem; --s3: 1.5rem; --s4: 2rem;
    --s6: 3rem;   --s8: 4rem; --s12: 6rem;  --s16: 8rem;
}

/* ============================================================
   RESET + BASE
   ============================================================ */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
}

body {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--c-bg);
    color: var(--c-white);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

@media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
    body { cursor: none; }
    .cursor-dot, .cursor-ring { display: block; }
}
@media (hover: none), (pointer: coarse) {
    .cursor-dot, .cursor-ring { display: none !important; }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        scroll-behavior: auto !important;
    }
    .cursor-dot, .cursor-ring { display: none !important; }
    #webgl-canvas { display: none !important; }
    body { cursor: auto !important; }
}

/* ============================================================
   CURSOR
   ============================================================ */
.cursor-dot {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--c-cyan); border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 9999;
    will-change: transform;
}
.cursor-ring {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 40px; height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.5); border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 9998;
    will-change: transform;
    transition: width 0.3s var(--ease-out),
                height 0.3s var(--ease-out),
                background-color 0.3s;
}

/* ============================================================
   PROGRESS BAR
   ============================================================ */
.progress-bar {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    height: 2px; background: var(--c-cyan);
    width: 0%; z-index: 200;
    transform-origin: left;
    transition: width 0.1s linear;
}

/* ============================================================
   WEBGL CANVAS
   ============================================================ */
#webgl-canvas {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100vw; height: 100vh;
    z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
}

/* ============================================================
   NAVIGATION
   ============================================================ */
nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%;
    height: var(--nav-h);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 0 5vw;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(3, 6, 12, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
}
.nav-brand {
    font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--c-white); text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 3vw;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
}
.nav-links a {
    color: var(--c-white); text-decoration: none;
    opacity: 0.7; transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a:focus-visible { opacity: 1; }

.nav-hamburger {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column; gap: 5px;
    background: none; border: none;
    cursor: pointer; padding: 8px;
    color: var(--c-white);
}
.nav-hamburger span {
    display: block; width: 24px; height: 1px;
    background: currentColor;
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-out), opacity 0.3s;
}
.nav-hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(6px) rotate(45deg); }
.nav-hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
.nav-hamburger[aria-expanded="true"] span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(-45deg); }

.nav-mobile-menu {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; top: var(--nav-h); left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: calc(100vh - var(--nav-h));
    background: rgba(3,6,12,0.97);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem; z-index: 99;
}
.nav-mobile-menu.is-open { display: flex; }
.nav-mobile-menu a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--c-white); text-decoration: none; opacity: 0.7;
}
.nav-mobile-menu a:hover { opacity: 1; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .nav-hamburger { display: flex; }
}

/* ============================================================
   FOCUS STYLES (accessibility)
   ============================================================ */
:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--c-cyan);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
}

/* ============================================================
   MAIN + SECTIONS
   ============================================================ */
main { position: relative; z-index: 10; }

section {
    width: 100%;
    padding: calc(var(--nav-h) + 6vw) 5vw 8vw;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}
section.hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding-top: var(--nav-h);
}

/* ============================================================
   TYPOGRAPHY
   ============================================================ */
h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 9vw, 11rem);
    font-weight: 100; letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    line-height: 0.85; margin: 0 0 var(--s4);
}
h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 6.5rem);
    font-weight: 100; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.95; margin: 0 0 var(--s4);
}
h3 {
    font-weight: 200;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 var(--s2);
}
p {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.1vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.65; max-width: 620px;
    font-weight: 200; opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0 0 var(--s3);
}

.outline-text {
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--c-muted);
}

.mono-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--s4); display: inline-block;
    padding: 5px 11px; border: 1px solid currentColor;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

/* ============================================================
   BUTTONS
   ============================================================ */
.btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--s2);
    padding: 1.1rem 2.2rem;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    background: transparent; color: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-decoration: none; border-radius: 40px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    transition: color 0.4s var(--ease-out);
}
.btn::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: currentColor;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-out);
    z-index: -1;
}
.btn:hover::before, .btn:focus-visible::before { transform: translateY(-100%); }
.btn:hover, .btn:focus-visible { color: var(--c-bg) !important; }

.btn-solid {
    background: var(--c-white); color: var(--c-bg);
}
.btn-solid::before { background: var(--c-bg); }
.btn-solid:hover, .btn-solid:focus-visible { color: var(--c-white) !important; }

.btn-cyan {
    border-color: var(--c-cyan); color: var(--c-cyan);
}
.btn-cyan::before { background: var(--c-cyan); }

.btn-group { display: flex; gap: var(--s2); margin-top: var(--s4); flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* ============================================================
   HERO SECTION
   ============================================================ */
.hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; }

.trust-strip {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--c-cyan);
    margin-top: var(--s12); display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem; opacity: 0.6; flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION THEMES
   ============================================================ */
.dark-sec { color: var(--c-white); background: transparent; }
.light-sec {
    color: var(--c-light-text);
    background: var(--c-light-bg);
}
.light-sec p { color: var(--c-light-text); }
.light-sec .btn:hover,
.light-sec .btn:focus-visible { color: var(--c-white) !important; }
.light-sec .btn-solid { color: var(--c-white); background: var(--c-bg); border-color: var(--c-bg); }
.light-sec .btn-solid::before { background: var(--c-white); }
.light-sec .btn-solid:hover { color: var(--c-bg) !important; }

/* ============================================================
   BIG BG TEXT (parallax atmosphere)
   ============================================================ */
.bg-giant-text {
    position: absolute; top: 5%; left: -3%;
    font-size: 22vw; font-weight: 100;
    line-height: 0.8; color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.025);
    pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    white-space: nowrap; user-select: none;
}
.light-sec .bg-giant-text {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px rgba(3,6,12,0.04);
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 2 — PROBLEM (split grid)
   ============================================================ */
.split-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8vw; align-items: center;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
}
.split-card {
    background: var(--c-light-bg);
    padding: var(--s8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(3,6,12,0.08);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}
.split-card p { max-width: none; }
.split-card h3 { margin-top: var(--s6); font-weight: 300; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .split-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s8); }
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 3 — OUTCOMES (centered cards)
   ============================================================ */
.outcomes-section {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; text-align: center;
}
.outcomes-header { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.symmetrical-outcomes {
    width: 100%; max-width: 900px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; gap: 5rem;
    position: relative; margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: 2rem;
}
.outcomes-divider {
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%;
    width: 1px; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        transparent,
        rgba(0,229,255,0.25),
        transparent
    );
    transform: translateX(-50%); z-index: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
}
.outcome-card {
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(2,6,13,0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding: 4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.5s var(--ease-out),
                border-color 0.5s,
                background 0.5s;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
}
.outcome-card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02) translateY(-8px);
    border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.35);
    background: rgba(0,229,255,0.03);
}
.outcome-card p { opacity: 0.55; transition: opacity 0.4s; margin: 0 auto; max-width: 600px; }
.outcome-card:hover p { opacity: 1; }
.outcome-card h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--s3);
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .outcome-card { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
    .symmetrical-outcomes { gap: 3rem; }
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 4 — CONCEPT WORK
   ============================================================ */
.s4-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8vw; align-items: end; margin-bottom: var(--s8);
}
.s4-header p { margin-bottom: 0; }

.concepts-wrapper {
    display: flex; gap: 2vw; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.concept-card {
    flex: 1; min-width: 280px; height: 480px;
    padding: var(--s6);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    perspective: 1000px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    overflow: hidden;
}
.concept-inner {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease-out);
}
.concept-card:hover .concept-inner { transform: translateZ(25px); }
.concept-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 100; line-height: 1; margin: 0;
}
.concept-meta h4 {
    font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
    .s4-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--s6); }
    .concept-card { min-width: 260px; height: 400px; }
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .concepts-wrapper { flex-direction: column; }
    .concept-card { min-width: unset; width: 100%; height: 360px; }
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 5 — PROCESS
   ============================================================ */
.process-header { max-width: 700px; margin-bottom: var(--s4); }

.process-timeline {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: var(--s8);
    padding-left: var(--s4);
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(3,6,12,0.15);
    max-width: 750px;
}
.timeline-progress {
    position: absolute; left: -1px; top: 0;
    width: 2px; height: 0%;
    background: var(--c-cyan);
    transition: height 0.1s linear;
}
.process-step {
    margin-bottom: var(--s12);
    position: relative; padding-left: var(--s6);
}
.process-step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.step-dot {
    position: absolute; left: calc(-1 * var(--s4));
    top: 1rem; width: 14px; height: 14px;
    background: var(--c-light-bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--c-cyan); border-radius: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    transition: transform 0.3s, background 0.3s;
}
.process-step:hover .step-dot {
    transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.5);
    background: var(--c-cyan);
}
.step-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--c-cyan); margin-bottom: var(--s2);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 6 — FIT
   ============================================================ */
.fit-header { margin-bottom: var(--s8); }

.fit-box-wrapper {
    display: flex; gap: 3vw; flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.fit-box {
    flex: 1; min-width: 300px;
    padding: var(--s8);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(3,6,12,0.1);
}
.fit-box.dark {
    background: var(--c-bg);
    color: var(--c-white);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}
.fit-box.light {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: rgba(3,6,12,0.08);
}
.fit-box-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 100; margin-bottom: var(--s6);
}
.fit-item {
    margin-bottom: var(--s4);
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.1vw, 1.1rem);
    font-weight: 200;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: var(--s2);
}
.fit-icon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .fit-box-wrapper { flex-direction: column; }
    .fit-box { min-width: unset; }
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTION 7 — CTA
   ============================================================ */
.cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    min-height: 80vh;
}
.cta-inner { max-width: 1000px; z-index: 2; position: relative; }
.cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 9rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--s4);
}
.cta-inner p {
    margin: 0 auto var(--s6);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.4rem);
    max-width: 550px;
}

/* ============================================================
   ANIMATION SETUP (motion allowed)
   ============================================================ */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .reveal-clip span { display: block; overflow: hidden; }
    .reveal-clip span > span {
        display: block;
        transform: translateY(110%);
        will-change: transform;
    }
    .fade-up {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(28px);
        will-change: opacity, transform;
    }
    .is-visible .reveal-clip span > span {
        animation: slideUp 1.1s var(--ease-out) forwards;
    }
    .is-visible.fade-up {
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s var(--ease-out) forwards;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
        to { transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* stagger siblings */
    .reveal-clip span:nth-child(1) > span { animation-delay: 0s; }
    .reveal-clip span:nth-child(2) > span { animation-delay: 0.08s; }
    .reveal-clip span:nth-child(3) > span { animation-delay: 0.16s; }

    .fade-up:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
    .fade-up:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
    .fade-up:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor-dot" id="cursorDot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar" role="progressbar" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<canvas id="webgl-canvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>

<nav role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
    <a href="/" class="nav-brand" aria-label="Solvus home">Solvus</a>
    <div class="nav-links" aria-label="Desktop navigation">
        <a href="#s4">Work</a>
        <a href="#s5">Process</a>
        <a href="#s7">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <button class="nav-hamburger" id="navToggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobileMenu" aria-label="Open navigation menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
</nav>

<div class="nav-mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu" role="dialog" aria-label="Mobile navigation" aria-modal="true">
    <a href="#s4" id="mobileWork">Work</a>
    <a href="#s5" id="mobileProcess">Process</a>
    <a href="#s7" id="mobileContact">Contact</a>
</div>

<main>

<section id="s1" class="hero dark-sec">
    <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="mono-label fade-up" style="color: var(--c-cyan); border-color: var(--c-cyan);">Solvus · Est. 2026</div>
        <h1 class="reveal-clip">
            <span><span>Top 1% in</span></span>
            <span><span class="outline-text">their market.</span></span>
        </h1>
        <p class="fade-up">Custom-built. Fast. Yours to keep. Built specifically for US real estate agents who are done renting templates.</p>
        <div class="btn-group fade-up">
            <a href="#s7" class="btn btn-solid hover-target">Book a 20-minute call ↗</a>
            <a href="#s4" class="btn btn-cyan hover-target">See the work</a>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-strip fade-up">
            <span>NAR Compliant</span>
            <span>MLS / IDX Ready</span>
            <span>Fair Housing Compliant</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="s2" class="light-sec">
    <div class="bg-giant-text para-text" aria-hidden="true">FAILURE</div>
    <div class="split-grid">
        <div style="padding-right: 2vw; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
            <div class="mono-label fade-up">01 / The Problem</div>
            <h2 class="reveal-clip">
                <span><span>Most realtor websites</span></span>
                <span><span>are built to sell to</span></span>
                <span><span>realtors, not buyers.</span></span>
            </h2>
            <p class="fade-up">Every Wix template, every Fiverr mockup, every broker-provided site is designed to look good in a sales pitch to an agent. Stock photos of happy couples. A Featured Listings grid no buyer will scroll. Six seconds to load.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="split-card fade-up">
            <p>Your buyers are not doing a tour of realtor websites. They are on their phone, on Zillow, with their partner in the passenger seat, trying to decide whether you are worth a phone call in the next twenty minutes.</p>
            <h3>That is a different product.<br>That is what we build.</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="s3" class="dark-sec outcomes-section">
    <div class="outcomes-header">
        <div class="mono-label fade-up" style="color: var(--c-cyan); border-color: var(--c-cyan);">02 / What You Get</div>
